72455043e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch will be passed around Greece in the next 11 days before it is handed over to the delegation of the organizing committee for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999997591942537, \"rank\": 2.4017971879200493e-07, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will depart Greece by ship for France on April 27.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999997591942537, \"rank\": 2.4017971879200493e-07, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9994609887700627, \"rank\": 0.0005020244480321773, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's Olympic Games, the 33rd edition of the tournament, will be the third time the Olympics are held in Paris, following the memorable editions of 1900 and 1924.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1648, \"entiti